sub_title: Staff Member Department of Cardiothoracic Anesthesiology at Leiden University Medical Center
summary: Experienced Anesthesiologist with a demonstrated history of working in the hospital & health care industry. Skilled in Clinical Research, Medical Education, Regional Anesthesia, Transesophageal Echocardiography, and Cardiothoracic and Pediatric Anesthesia. Strong healthcare services professional graduated from European Association of Echocardiography. Currently executing PhD project on cardiovascular effects of thoracic epidural anesthesia
